<h1 class="h3 mb-3">about this project</h1>
<p>this app collects brewery data and links it to countries. it demonstrates data import, associations, search, pagination, and basic maps.</p>

<h2 class="h5 mt-4">data sources</h2>
<ul>
  <li>rest countries api for country data at runtime or faker fallback</li>
  <li>open brewery db api for brewery data at runtime or faker fallback</li>
  <li>faker gem for supplemental seed data</li>
</ul>

